{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.720", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.720", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.240", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sprechen heute \u00fcber einen mutma\u00dflichen Fall der Korruption beim Bundesamt f\u00fcr Migration und Fl\u00fcchtlinge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.920", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der nach jetzigem Kenntnisstand dazu gef\u00fchrt hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass vermutlich Tausende von positiven Asylbescheiden gegen geltendes Recht versto\u00dfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.800", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das genaue Ausma\u00df dieses Rechtsbruchs und auch die genaue Anzahl der daran beteiligten Mitarbeiter sind zum derzeitigen Zeitpunkt nicht abschlie\u00dfend zu bewerten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.480", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist es richtig und auch wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.360", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich das Parlament heute mit diesem Fall besch\u00e4ftigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.000", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier muss selbstverst\u00e4ndlich schonungslos und vollumf\u00e4nglich Aufkl\u00e4rung betrieben werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.280", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allem die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.160", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum ein solch massenhafter Rechtsbruch nicht im Rahmen der BAMF-internen \u00dcberpr\u00fcfungen aufgefallen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern erst durch einen externen Hinweis zur Kenntnis genommen wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.080", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss gekl\u00e4rt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings erweckt die Fokussierung auf diesen Vorfall den Eindruck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es sich hier nur um einen fast schon marginalen Einzelfall handele und dass ansonsten die Asylentscheidungen des BAMF weder unter rechtsstaatlichen noch unter sicherheitspolitischen Aspekten zu beanstanden seien. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber genau das ist falsch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.360", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die heutige Einzelbetrachtung geht am Kern des Problems vorbei."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.600", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung hat sich entschlossen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.080", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die deutschen Grenzen zu \u00f6ffnen und Hunderttausende Menschen illegal ins Land zu lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.480", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit dieser fatalen Entscheidung hat die Regierung daf\u00fcr gesorgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Bundesamt f\u00fcr Migration und Fl\u00fcchtlinge aufgrund der schieren Masse an Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.480", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es pl\u00f6tzlich bearbeiten musste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.440", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "total \u00fcberfordert war. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.480", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Tatsache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.480", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass bis zu 80\u00a0Prozent der sogenannten Fl\u00fcchtlinge ohne Papiere in unser Land kamen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.480", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat dazu gef\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine verl\u00e4ssliche \u00dcberpr\u00fcfung der Identit\u00e4t und der Fluchtgeschichte f\u00fcr die BAMF-Mitarbeiter gar nicht m\u00f6glich war."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei Asylverfahren waren nicht mehr objektiv nachpr\u00fcfbare Fakten die Grundlage der Entscheidung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern allein die m\u00fcndliche Angabe des Asylbewerbers, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die war meist auch noch von eilig beauftragten Dolmetschern mit fragw\u00fcrdiger Qualifikation abh\u00e4ngig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.680", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotz der mittlerweile umgesetzten effizienzverbessernden Ma\u00dfnahmen hat sich an den Grunds\u00e4tzen dieses Verfahrens nichts ge\u00e4ndert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies l\u00e4sst sich treffend mit dem Satz zusammenfassen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Asylentscheidungen des Bundesamtes f\u00fcr Migration und Fl\u00fcchtlinge galt und gilt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00e4rchenstunde statt Faktencheck."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.200", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn noch immer kommt die Mehrzahl der Fl\u00fcchtlinge ohne Identit\u00e4tspapiere in unser Land, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und noch immer sind unsere Grenzen f\u00fcr jeden Asylsuchenden sperrangelweit ge\u00f6ffnet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.560", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hat mit einem Asylverfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das rechtsstaatlichen Grunds\u00e4tzen gen\u00fcgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.400", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nichts zu tun."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.960", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr ist allein diese Regierung verantwortlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.480", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch unter Sicherheitsaspekten muss dieser Irrweg schnellstens korrigiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bitte die Regierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.640", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Mayer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.480", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "inst\u00e4ndig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.440", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zur Kenntnis zu nehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ohne Identit\u00e4tspapiere eine verl\u00e4ssliche Sicherheits\u00fcberpr\u00fcfung einer Person schlicht nicht m\u00f6glich ist; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn auch Plausibilit\u00e4tspr\u00fcfungen und diesbez\u00fcglich erg\u00e4nzende Ma\u00dfnahmen belegen keineswegs die Identit\u00e4t einer Person, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.400", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sie lassen sie lediglich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie der Name schon sagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "plausibel erscheinen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.680", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das Erheben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.280", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Speichern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.560", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abgleichen biometrischer Daten bringt keinen Sicherheitsgewinn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.560", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Terroristen oder Gewaltt\u00e4ter in den polizeilichen Systemen noch gar nicht erfasst sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.560", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich darf Sie daran erinnern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.360", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Anis Amri als Fl\u00fcchtling in dieses Land eingereist ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die neu geschaffene Norm zur Auswertung von Mobiltelefonen hilft nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.760", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sicherheitslage wirklich nachhaltig zu verbessern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Sie n\u00e4mlich die Tatbestandsvoraussetzungen so eng gefasst haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie viel zu selten zur Anwendung kommt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.240", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um wirklich etwas zu bewirken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.000", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcsste sie als Standardma\u00dfnahme bei Asylsuchenden ohne Identit\u00e4tspapiere angewandt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.160", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Ergebnis bedeutet dies: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.840", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie halten mit dem derzeitigen Verfahren trotz aller Neuerungen keine Terroristen und Gewaltt\u00e4ter auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies belegt eindeutig die st\u00e4ndig wachsende Zahl der islamistischen Gef\u00e4hrder und Salafisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.880", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich rate dem Innenminister und vielleicht auch dem einen oder anderen Staatssekret\u00e4r, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.240", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zur Erkenntnisgewinnung nicht nur Gespr\u00e4che mit Beh\u00f6rdenleitungen zu f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.280", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch einmal mit Polizeibeamten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.840", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die operativ in diesem Bereich t\u00e4tig sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.600", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die werden Ihnen das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.480", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was ich hier ausgef\u00fchrt habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "definitiv best\u00e4tigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.480", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb bedarf es dringend einer politischen Kurskorrektur. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.040", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich fordere deshalb die Bundesregierung auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.880", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich effektiv unsere Grenzen zu sch\u00fctzen und Personen ohne Identit\u00e4tspapiere konsequent zur\u00fcckzuweisen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss der Grundsatz gelten: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.040", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer ohne Identit\u00e4tspapiere einreisen will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.520", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "betritt unser Land nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.000", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit reduzieren Sie die Fl\u00fcchtlingszahlen erheblich und sorgen daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "298.440", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das BAMF seiner origin\u00e4ren Aufgabe wieder nachkommen kann und auf der Grundlage fundierter Fakten seine Entscheidungen trifft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "298.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.040", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allem aber ist effektiver Grenzschutz absolut notwendig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "307.560", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Sicherheitslage in unserem Land wirksam und nachhaltig zu verbessern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "307.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.600", 
   "id": "s000084", 
